"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"on9 條女咪又係要去counter搞返張八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1b0189006609cb92bc631e53717e7b83cdbbac","tid":830713,"uid":126720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:18:12.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯佢下次會入唔到閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67af9bf7f66ccf9fcbf287ad24ba898691358257","tid":830713,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"唔記得攞電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879d81950f2a61b20b92f6036f720d4598414bda","tid":830713,"uid":90595,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:19:21.000Z","msg":"我係一張八達通，今日如常比主人嘟我入閘，但出閘時主人嘟錯左另一張卡，搞到出唔到閘｡<br />\n隱約聽到有個輕度弱智嘅痴漢話咩「得啦呢到我搞掂，你走先」｡<br />\n後尾主人同男朋友開完房搭地鐵走，拍我入唔到閘，要去客務中心，搞到我比人陌生人摸反轉再反轉｡<br />\n比我知條弱智囝係邊個，我實屌到佢仆街｡"},{"pid":"c3e7b3df479acf6b3a77308b39bfbc059fa0f53a","tid":830713,"uid":149496,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:19:23.000Z","msg":"大家好 我係部閘機 <br />\n<br />\n今日返工嗰陣又有個白痴港女 臨出閘先黎攞張八達通出黎 係到阻鳩住晒<br />\n<br />\n又有個白痴仔懶醒 諗住條女八達通唔夠錢 可以英雄救美<br />\n<br />\n點知個白痴仔冇啦啦一野拍落黎 屌你老母 痛撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n白痴仔:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  白痴港女 :<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我請你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 下...但係...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 得啦, 呢度等我搞掂 你走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後個白痴仔一野推條白痴港女出閘 咁大力又好撚痛<br />\n<br />\n屌晒你兩條白痴個老母"},{"pid":"9ecbd11ad34e6c404858c8db3273db955b96e6d1","tid":830713,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0